# AchekBot - WhatsApp Bot

## Overview
AchekBot is a powerful WhatsApp bot built with Node.js and the Baileys library. This backend application connects to WhatsApp to manage groups, automate tasks, and respond to commands. Powered by **Achek Digital Solutions**.

**Version**: 4.0.0  
**Bot Name**: AchekBot  
**Owner**: Caleb  
**Business**: Achek Digital Solutions  
**Website**: https://achek.com.ng

## Project Type
This is a **backend-only application** - there is no frontend or web interface. The bot operates through WhatsApp messages and displays console logs for monitoring.

